    article
      h2.font-bold.text-lg
        i.fa-solid.fa-calendar.fa-fw.text-emerald-500.mr-2
        | Subscribing to the calendar
      p.text-lg You can add the #{@unit.name} schedule to your favorite calendar app by subscribing to the calendar:
   
    article
      h2.font-bold.text-lg
        i.fa-solid.fa-calendar.fa-fw.text-emerald-500.mr-2
